            "title": "Roost selection in the pipistrelle bat,Pipistrellus pipistrellus(Chiroptera: Vespertilionidae), in northeast Scotland",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "E.V",
                    "lastName": "Jenkins"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
